      "title": "<span id=\"#25861\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">centre</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\"></div></span>",
      "html": "<p>主要用于英国英语的拼写方式，参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of center \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/center\">center</a>（请参阅）； 有关结尾，请参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -re \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-re\">-re</a>。</p>"
